About – Carolco Pictures


















































 
 










1
Carolco is an entertainment technology company that is redefining media consumption. We are focused on creating disruptive software and developing original film, television and immersive content.
In June 2016, new management was put in place. The team, led by seasoned entertainment and technology executives, is committed to achieiving significant growth through acquisitions and production.
Carolco’s first strategic acquisition was purchasing Recall Studios in the 3rd quarter of 2016. Recall is developing a ground breaking platform that will change the way filmmakers create experiences and how viewers interact with content.


