Carolco Pictures Inc.


            
            Carolco Pictures, Inc. is an entertainment technology company. It is focused on creating disruptive software and developing original film, television and immersive content. The company was founded by Alexander C. Bafer and Christopher Leone on February 20, 2009 and is headquartered in Boca Raton, FL.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


